So, I downloaded some mods and completely re-installed KSP. When I added the mods and go in to the VAB or SPH there are no parts or anything to use. Can anybody make suggestions as to how to fix this? Thanks.

KAX 2.3.4

Near Future Solar 0.4.0

Remote Tech 1.6.3

Karbonite 0.5.5

MKS 0.22.6

NavHud 1.1.4

MechJeb 2.4.2.0

SCANsat 10

Module Manager 2.6.9

Firespitter 7

The version of Community Resource Pack, USITools, and Regolith Karbonite and MKS came with. (No, I did not install anything twice by mistake).

https://docs.google.com/document/d/1J1J4x5WH8BAwBcn0JYNZ9tFc0p8i7CK6T33WfxNToFA/edit

I figured out the error. There was a firespitter file that came with MKS and one that came with KAX. I used the one that came with MKS, but it turns out there was a file that KAX needs that was in its firespitter file, causing it to nullref when it didn't have it, so I tried that one and it works now . Thanks anyway guys
Well, now you'll have problems with MKS. But I think MKS uses the latest dev edition of Firespitter... are you sure you use the latest version of MKS?
